  "text": "The idea of using geometrical parameters in FR prediction is not new. Supplementary geometrical parameters were applied for the antero-posterior (AP) aBMD aiming at the improvement of FR prediction [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . Several authors have proposed to utilize certain geometrical parameters as independent variables related to FR [CITATION_6] [CITATION_7] .",
